description: Enjoy the pinnacle of luxury at Twenty Two Liberty in Boston's Seaport. This stunning corner residence boasts two bedrooms plus a large den with breathtaking views of Boston Harbor and the city skyline throughout. Floor-to-ceiling walls of glass frame the brilliant surroundings and flood the home with natural light. At the center, an open-concept living and dining space connects to a spacious private terrace directly overlooking the harbor. Ideal for any occasion, the chef's kitchen is outfitted with top-of-the-line appliances from Sub Zero, Miele, and Wolfe, as well as an adjacent walk-in pantry. The primary suite features stunning water views, a large walk-in closet, and a marble-clad bathroom with a glass-enclosed shower and soaking tub. An en suite guest bedroom and a bonus room that can be used as a well-appointed home office offer ample space for flexible living. Two garage spaces complete this extraordinary residence, set in one of the Seaport's most sought-after addresses.
